# MAD-T02-Team-6 (Updated as of 28/07/2020)
Title of App: Boba Check!

//Made by:
1. Ben Chang (S10185167D)
2. Lim Wei Hao (S10185304A)
3. Akid Qusyairi (S10194941K)

//Description of App:
An app that can help you satisfy your bubble tea need while helping you keep a healthy lifestyle. 
You can browse through the different bubble tea drinks offered by different bubble tea shops such as KOI, Gong Cha and LIHO
Check where the nearest bubble tea stores are at and buy a bubble tea drink hassle-free.
You can also set a spending limit to help you keep track of your bubble tea consumption.

//Roles and contributions:
Menu (Akid)
Browse through a compiled menu containing 15+ bubble tea drinks made by popular bubble tea shops such as KOI, Gong Cha and LiHo.
Click on each menu item to find out more about the breakdown of the calories in the drink.

Location (Ben)
Craving for bubble tea but unsure of where the nearest bubble tea store is at? Fret not! Our app has a location feature
that gives real-time data of where each bubble tea shop is at. Just simply scroll through the list of shops
and you will be able to quickly find a store that is nearest to your house.

Tracker (Wei Hao)
Addicted to bubble tea drinks? The Tracker feature is here to keep your cravings in check!
Set a spending limit for bubble tea drinks every month to take note of how much you spent.
Add purchases in the app to reflect how much money you spent on bubble tea drinks so far.

